{"tid":288453,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙14日行程 求指教","createTime":"2017-06-18T08:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T12:38:31.000Z","uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f1881e51eeb8190fb38a4364bda9e8de8d5198","tid":288453,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:03:56.000Z","msg":"下個月會去西班牙14日 飛馬德里 巴塞翻 <br />\n打算預留大部分時間係巴塞個邊，想問一下巴絲有咩行程推介同注意事項，特別係應唔應該留幾日去馬略卡島/ibiza個邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫定行程，景點有興趣再分享，希望到時開到live<br />\n4 days: 馬德里<br />\n1 day: toledo<br />\n2 days: 西維爾<br />\n7 days: 巴塞羅那"},{"pid":"aed45936f03aae95da10044155ec4d8cbde34e07","tid":288453,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c69087d8c22168598ebac5d00fc49da5c6729a","tid":288453,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c3170c97355ba17ef07ffac79f82c7e4c18edd14","tid":288453,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:10:07.000Z","msg":"馬德里2日夠<br />\n睇埋皇馬"},{"pid":"eeb4352eb9ca96a56c1dec5c75bb1cbff76eec11","tid":288453,"uid":14980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/162312_a4835154da90bdb2b644333ba7aac0b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F162312_a4835154da90bdb2b644333ba7aac0b3.jpg&h=18509c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打夠晒時間 分多一日去Granada<br />\n近Sevilla"},{"pid":"40395d993c5e75d78ad9be28e5565101bc2d8011","tid":288453,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/162312_a4835154da90bdb2b644333ba7aac0b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F162312_a4835154da90bdb2b644333ba7aac0b3.jpg&h=18509c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打夠晒時間 分多一日去Granada<br />\n近Sevilla</blockquote><br />\n上網睇啲人去親西班牙都俾人偷野 巴打知唔知係咪真係咁癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525c6fdea4736021e2ec349cee52899722e10f12","tid":288453,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:52:57.000Z","msg":"Bcn3 days Madrid + Segovia Toledo 3 days <br />\nCordoba 2 days<br />\nGranada 2 days<br />\nSeville + Ronda 3 days<br />\nLisbon 2 days<br />\n我上次大約係咁"},{"pid":"e0652d75f9cf20cc6bb0ec4a99ad606f941ea6e1","tid":288453,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:54:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Bcn3 days Madrid + Segovia Toledo 3 days <br />\nCordoba 2 days<br />\nGranada 2 days<br />\nSeville + Ronda 3 days<br />\nLisbon 2 days<br />\n我上次大約係咁</blockquote><br />\n補充一下 Granada最正 <br />\nMadrid悶<br />\n自己小心d就ok 唔覺好多小偷"},{"pid":"ad69c93fb581beedfb50a3d83b9e82290ea306be","tid":288453,"uid":117114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"大城市小偷多, <br />\n證件放在貼身腰包揾件衫遮住<br />\n<br />\n馬德里可以唔洗留咁耐, <br />\n如果留四日可以day trip 去吓Aranjuez/Sergovia"},{"pid":"f54986e7696766ec15f478c0686eca80d35f4457","tid":288453,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:23:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/162312_a4835154da90bdb2b644333ba7aac0b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F162312_a4835154da90bdb2b644333ba7aac0b3.jpg&h=18509c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打夠晒時間 分多一日去Granada<br />\n近Sevilla</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nalhambra 真係好值得去<br />\n入去主宮入面要好早登記<br />\n上次一個月前book已經冇位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後買咗granada card先入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2330fbe3af59fd3e5d67d07bab6ca03d526f29dc","tid":288453,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"4日馬德里悶到你仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fa310bd31f6de4000f9a1a30c091d7d3c15905","tid":288453,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"另外同意馬德里可以唔留咁耐<br />\n四日可以day trip去Segovia 同 Toledo<br />\n不過馬德里淨係 prado， reina Sofia 睇 Guernica，王宮都可以睇好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f221fa72c318eb179c6376070fc809cacedfc6bf","tid":288453,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:31:43.000Z","msg":"如果去granada可以睇吓有冇過夜火車去巴塞羅納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f060caefccc099ee883c3ef14254c1a0514b7ea6","tid":288453,"uid":18425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"最好去埋lisbon, Gibraltar<br />\n<br />\n有時候參考旅行社路線都係一個唔錯既方法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/203544_5380c93dd8a79976bf0124e6203a0cc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F203544_5380c93dd8a79976bf0124e6203a0cc1.jpg&h=88a0c6d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52b68b46e34f7c6cbd9a2b561e24e79fa2fb8458","tid":288453,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最好去埋lisbon, Gibraltar<br />\n<br />\n有時候參考旅行社路線都係一個唔錯既方法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/18/203544_5380c93dd8a79976bf0124e6203a0cc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2F203544_5380c93dd8a79976bf0124e6203a0cc1.jpg&h=88a0c6d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該絲打 但成個trip打算預兩萬only  我諗冇乜budget 去葡萄牙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac260946a4f83b3b5ba4e69660400f0e12e0ffc","tid":288453,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"另外聽左好多巴絲已經打算直接skip左馬德里，因為其實去馬德里淨係想去班拿貝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家咁可能巴塞去巴塞翻玩落去華倫西亞同馬略卡島<br />\n<br />\nSevilla 同直布羅陀同葡就可能要留翻下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c918f07d6c4a96f0c334605ecc25236bc4aa16cd","tid":288453,"uid":60166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"巴塞市內5日一定夠，除非好鍾意玩沙灘"},{"pid":"9a93b6484240d15c28f2bb693bcb7137f8af1860","tid":288453,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外聽左好多巴絲已經打算直接skip左馬德里，因為其實去馬德里淨係想去班拿貝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家咁可能巴塞去巴塞翻玩落去華倫西亞同馬略卡島<br />\n<br />\nSevilla 同直布羅陀同葡就可能要留翻下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMadrid 1-2日(去toledo/segovia/cuanca)<br />\nSevilla 2-3日<br />\nMalaga/ Granada 2-3日<br />\nValencia 2-3日<br />\nBarca 4-5日<br />\n<br />\n係皇迷就點都去班拿貝參觀下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都值既 咁係馬德里留1-2日"},{"pid":"53b792c3574a9fd96b7d5528cb0091bede5dbebf","tid":288453,"uid":29859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T14:49:26.000Z","msg":"去巴塞去高迪啲建築物就梗架啦 見到會有wow一聲既感覺 尤其是聖家堂 記得要上塔頂 巴打一定要朝聖！<br />\n如果想去郊外可以唸下用一日去Montserrat 係巴塞坐大概個半鐘 但個到風景都唔錯 一點幾會有童聲聖詩班唱歌 聽人講好正 但我今次miss左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬德里我留左2日 如果唔係去睇鬥牛我都唔會去 鬥牛睇唔睇就因人而異啦 因為有啲環保人士會嘈 唔知樓主有冇朋友好關注呢樣野 但Sevilla就好似岀名啲<br />\n有樣野要留意既係 巴塞市中心既超市同百貨公司星期日係唔開門 就係因為咁我冇咩點買手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打自己夾翻時間行下買手信啦<br />\n利申啱啱去完翻黎都冇一個禮拜"},{"pid":"2c6c10540da53f8dec373e067bd1522479b42f62","tid":288453,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去巴塞去高迪啲建築物就梗架啦 見到會有wow一聲既感覺 尤其是聖家堂 記得要上塔頂 巴打一定要朝聖！<br />\n如果想去郊外可以唸下用一日去Montserrat 係巴塞坐大概個半鐘 但個到風景都唔錯 一點幾會有童聲聖詩班唱歌 聽人講好正 但我今次miss左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬德里我留左2日 如果唔係去睇鬥牛我都唔會去 鬥牛睇唔睇就因人而異啦 因為有啲環保人士會嘈 唔知樓主有冇朋友好關注呢樣野 但Sevilla就好似岀名啲<br />\n有樣野要留意既係 巴塞市中心既超市同百貨公司星期日係唔開門 就係因為咁我冇咩點買手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打自己夾翻時間行下買手信啦<br />\n利申啱啱去完翻黎都冇一個禮拜</blockquote><br />\n星期日一般商鋪都唔開 歐洲都係咁<br />\n巴塞都算好 有士多仲可以買野食 手信鋪都應該開<br />\n其他地區問題仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd8874071fe9840eb21a69d10a7bc83eef216e1","tid":288453,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T15:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去巴塞去高迪啲建築物就梗架啦 見到會有wow一聲既感覺 尤其是聖家堂 記得要上塔頂 巴打一定要朝聖！<br />\n如果想去郊外可以唸下用一日去Montserrat 係巴塞坐大概個半鐘 但個到風景都唔錯 一點幾會有童聲聖詩班唱歌 聽人講好正 但我今次miss左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬德里我留左2日 如果唔係去睇鬥牛我都唔會去 鬥牛睇唔睇就因人而異啦 因為有啲環保人士會嘈 唔知樓主有冇朋友好關注呢樣野 但Sevilla就好似岀名啲<br />\n有樣野要留意既係 巴塞市中心既超市同百貨公司星期日係唔開門 就係因為咁我冇咩點買手信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打自己夾翻時間行下買手信啦<br />\n利申啱啱去完翻黎都冇一個禮拜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔該哂巴打 太血腥小女子頂唔緊<img sr